<HEADLINE>
FOR SOME, A FIELD OF DREAMS CAN BE A NIGHTMARE 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Ore.)  (Eds., also filed in `s' category)  
(rk) 
 By IVER PETERSON   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
