<P>
   KOSOVO-ALBANIA _ TIRANA, Albania _ Albania, The United States'
new best friend, apparently has horrendous human rights practices
including locking up death-row inmates in iron masks and suspending
them from the wall during the day. This falls under the category of
our strange new bedfellow of convenience. Developing. (Roughton,
Cox News Service). 30. WITH PHOTO. MOVED
</P>
<P>
